description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Long Term Placement Opportunity Available&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Registered Nurse – Nurse Team Leader Mental Health (Community Hospital&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you a Registered Mental Health Team Leader seeking a placement? Do you want to make a difference to patients quality of life?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We currently have a unique and exciting opportunity within &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Southern Health NHS Foundation Trust&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; which will allow the successful candidates to gain &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;regular shifts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; and valuable &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;experience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; within a unique &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;mental health&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; environment. We have a &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Long Term Placement opportunity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; available within at Gosport War Memorial – Hewat Centre, providing you with the chance to work &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;regular shifts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; for a &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;guaranteed period of 3 months on a rolling contract&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location: Gosport War Memorial Hospital, Gosport&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Band 6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Day Rate - £19.38 per hour &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Night/Sat Rate - £25.19 per hour&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sun/Bank Holiday Rate - £31.00 per hour&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NHS Professionals, is working in conjunction with Southern Health NHS Foundation trust who are seeking qualified Registered Mental Health Team Leaders to join the bank working at the Hewat Centre. NHS Professionals works in partnership with Southern Health NHS Foundation Trust to provide their temporary staffing requirements. We are seeking Registered Team Leaders to work 37.5 hours a week Monday to Friday from 09:00am to 17:00pm.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking Registered Team Leaders to work at Gosport War Memorial Hospital - The Community Mental Health Team is based in Gosport and offers a range of treatments and therapies to support recovery with access to Early Intervention in Psychosis (EIP).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be offered a full induction, training and development opportunities and a fully flexible approach to hours – full or part time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In order to apply for a post you &lt;strong&gt;must&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Have a minimum of 6 months experience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; in a similar role held within the last 2 years&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have good communication skills and demonstrate evidence of team working&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be able to take direction and instruction and be honest and trustworthy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In return for your hard work and your professional, caring and reliable service you will have access to the following benefits:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive, weekly pay&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to the NHSP Stakeholder Pension&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paid annual leave and statutory maternity pay (subject to qualifying criteria)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Training and development opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;First refusal on available shifts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like more information or an informal discussion, please contact The Southern Health Bank Team on: SHFTRecruitment@nhsprofessionals.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note that you will be contacted via email throughout the recruitment process, so we urge you to ensure your email address submitted is accurate and checked regularly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We regret we cannot contact everyone who is not selected for an interview, therefore if you do not hear from us within 21 days after submitting your application, please assume you have not been successful on this occasion.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Registration with NHS Professionals is subject to employment history and reference checking and offers of registration are therefore conditional upon the receipt of satisfactory references&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
